WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:10.260 --> 00:00:18.290
Good evening. This is Tomo from the Oyasumi Japanese Channel.

00:00:18.290 --> 00:00:31.000
Today, I will share what might be the shortest Japanese folktale.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:35.090
Please listen.

00:00:35.090 --> 00:00:40.210
[The Smell Thief] / Nioi Dorobo

00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:59.290
Long, long ago, there was an eel shop in a certain town.

00:00:59.290 --> 00:01:15.100
Next door lived a man who had no money.

00:01:15.100 --> 00:01:30.080
The man could not afford to buy any eel.

00:01:30.080 --> 00:01:44.010
So, he would just smell the delicious scent from the eel shop

00:01:44.010 --> 00:01:57.000
and eat his plain white rice.

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:14.290
Every day, he enjoyed his rice using only the smell of the eel.

00:02:14.290 --> 00:02:31.070
One day, the owner of the eel shop got angry and said:

00:02:31.070 --> 00:02:52.110
"You! You've been smelling my food every day. Pay me for the smell!"

00:02:52.110 --> 00:03:04.080
The man was very troubled.

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:21.110
Just then, a wise official arrived.

00:03:21.110 --> 00:03:32.010
"I will pay for him," he said.

00:03:32.010 --> 00:03:46.270
The official took out a few coins.

00:03:46.270 --> 00:04:06.230
Then, he jangled them in his hand to make a sound.

00:04:06.230 --> 00:04:27.070
"That sound is the payment for the smell. A sound is a fair price for a smell, isn't it?"

00:04:27.070 --> 00:04:40.050
The eel shop owner was speechless.

00:04:40.050 --> 00:04:49.140
He quietly went back inside his shop.

00:04:49.140 --> 00:04:55.020
The end.

00:04:55.020 --> 00:05:07.070
How do you think the shop owner felt when he heard the sound of the money?

00:05:07.070 --> 00:05:13.280
That was a very clever and funny story, wasn't it?

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:31.260
Now, here is a question. How did the official pay the shop owner?

00:05:31.260 --> 00:05:45.170
[1. With real money]  [2. With the sound of money]

00:05:45.170 --> 00:05:55.260
The answer is in the comments. Please check it.

00:05:55.260 --> 00:06:03.270
Well then, good night. Sweet dreams.

